- given a username (author), repo url, and start version:
  - will monitor repo for commits
  - for each new commit:
    - for each file in the commit:
      - step through previous commits for given file, backwards, looking for author of all adjacent or overlapping changed lines
      - if author is the author we're monitoring, then add this change to the set of change the author needs to be notified of
    - if any changes exist for the author, notify the author
